      ii @KJ{{before^life}}mo @KJ{{many}}ishi, <strong>soreni</strong>@KJ{{house}}kara
      @KJ{{near}}idesukara.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      A: Why did you choose Sakura Univeristy?
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      B: Because it is my father's alma mater, there are many good teachers, and besides, it's near my house.
  </td> </tr>
